      <title>特朗普誓言“扣押”国会拨款。他能做到吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/impoundment-can-trump-refuse-to-spend-money-congress-appropriates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他有很多方法可以缩减联邦政府规模：取消教育部；授权两个富有的盟友成立一个非官方的政府效率部；削减监管政府的官僚机构。还有一个想法：不要把国会让他花的钱全部花掉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/impoundment-can-trump-refuse-to-spend-money-congress-appropriates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲商业团体调查发现中国挑战日益严峻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/european-business-groups-surveys-find-rising-china-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两项最新调查显示，英国和德国企业在中国开展业务的日子越来越难过，而且他们对明年的前景感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/european-business-groups-surveys-find-rising-china-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>六小时戒严如何改变震惊的韩国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/how-six-hours-of-martial-law-reshaped-a-stunned-south-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，一个气温接近零度的夜晚，快到晚上 10 点的时候，记者中间开始流传谣言，说韩国总统尹锡烈计划在深夜宣布消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/how-six-hours-of-martial-law-reshaped-a-stunned-south-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行行长李承晚表示，鉴于尹富比的惊人举动，降息的可能性不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bok-chief-rhee-says-unlikely-to-cut-rates-on-political-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行行长李昌镕表示，央行不太可能降息，他淡化了总统尹锡烈实施戒严令所引发的政治混乱对经济的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bok-chief-rhee-says-unlikely-to-cut-rates-on-political-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 08:37:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国港口雇主称自动化是劳工谈判的“核心”优先事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/us-port-employers-call-automation-core-priority-in-labor-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国东部和墨西哥湾沿岸港口码头的集装箱运输公司和运营商表示，如果这意味着放弃投资半自动化货物处理设备的权利，他们将不会继续与工会码头工人就新的六年合同进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/us-port-employers-call-automation-core-priority-in-labor-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 08:19:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工党启动三条铁路国有化计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/uk-s-labour-kicks-off-nationalization-with-three-train-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党政府将把目前由私营部门运营的三项火车服务收归国有，这是将该行业重新掌握在公共手中的计划的开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/uk-s-labour-kicks-off-nationalization-with-three-train-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 08:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国前贸易部长称尹永哲犯下严重错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/yoon-made-grave-mistake-says-former-south-korean-trade-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国前贸易部长批评总统尹锡烈颁布戒严令的错误决定，该决定引发了公众的强烈抗议并震动了全球金融市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/yoon-made-grave-mistake-says-former-south-korean-trade-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 07:39:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾副总统杜特尔特面临第二次弹劾指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/philippines-vp-duterte-faces-second-impeachment-complaint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾副总统萨拉·杜特尔特遭到第二起弹劾指控，这是她与总统小费迪南德·马科斯公开争吵后引发的政治危机的最新进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/philippines-vp-duterte-faces-second-impeachment-complaint</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 07:29:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国政党试图弹劾尹永哲，进一步孤立他</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-opposition-party-seeks-to-impeach-yoon-for-treason-m49amyj3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈短暂实施戒严令，导致国家陷入政治危机。此后，韩国反对派提出弹劾动议，加大了对他的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-opposition-party-seeks-to-impeach-yoon-for-treason-m49amyj3</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 02:53:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
